title: So You Think You Can Dance US S11E05
description:
SO YOU THINK YOU CAN DANCE US S11E05
Air Date: Wednesday, June 25, 2014
Time Slot: 8:00 PM-10:00 PM EST on FOX
Episode Title: (DAN-1105) "Pasadena Callbacks"

The search continues tonight for America's Favorite Dancer as SO YOU THINK YOU CAN DANCE heads to Pasadena for callbacks. See what happens when the best dancers from all five audition cities compete in the grueling callbacks for a coveted spot in the Top 20. See who leaps into the judges' hearts and who falls flat in the all-new "Pasadena Callbacks" episode of SO YOU THINK YOU CAN DANCE airing Wednesday, June 25 (8:00-10:00 PM ET/PT) on FOX. (DAN-1105) (TV-14 D, L)

Host: Cat Deeley

Judges: Nigel Lythgoe, Mary Murphy

Guest Judges: Adam Shankman, Stephen "tWitch" Boss, Tara Lipinski, Irina Dvorovenko
